title: Stanford’s Ronnie Harris helping David Shaw come out of his shell
text:
Photo: John J. Kim, McClatchy-Tribune News Service Fifth-year senior cornerback Ronnie Harris is training to be a mental-health professional. Fifth-year senior cornerback Ronnie Harris is training to be a...
David Shaw isn’t nearly as demonstrative on the sideline as many other college football coaches. But he has taken great strides toward showing his emotions — thanks to would-be shrink Ronnie Harris.
